Based on my analysis, the new administrative unit for "Xã Ba Cụm Bắc, Huyện Khánh Sơn, Tỉnh Khánh Hòa" is "Xã Đông Khánh Sơn".  The "province_name" remains "Tỉnh Khánh Hòa".  I have a high level of confidence in this result because the mapping is explicitly stated in the relevant resolution.
